#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:3
msgid "Code of Conduct"
msgstr "行为准则"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:6
msgid "Our Pledge"
msgstr "我们的承诺"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:8
msgid ""
"We as members, contributors, and leaders pledge to make participation in "
"our community a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of "
"age, body size, visible or invisible disability, ethnicity, sex "
"characteristics, gender identity and expression, level of experience, "
"education, socio-economic status, nationality, personal appearance, race,"
" religion, or sexual identity and orientation."
msgstr ""
"我们作为成员、贡献者和领导者，承诺为每个人提供无骚扰的社区参与体验，"
"无论年龄、体型、可见或不可见的残疾、种族、性别特征、"
"性别认同和表达、经验水平、教育程度、社会经济地位、"
"国籍、个人外貌、种族、宗教或性身份和取向。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:10
msgid ""
"We pledge to act and interact in ways that contribute to an open, "
"welcoming, diverse, inclusive, and healthy community."
msgstr ""
"我们承诺以有助于建立开放、热情、多元、包容和健康社区的方式行事和互动。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:13
msgid "Our Standards"
msgstr "我们的标准"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:15
msgid ""
"Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment for our "
"community include:"
msgstr "有助于为我们社区营造积极环境的行为示例包括："

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:18
msgid "Demonstrating empathy and kindness toward other people"
msgstr "对他人表现出同理心和善意"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:19
msgid "Being respectful of differing opinions, viewpoints, and experiences"
msgstr "尊重不同的意见、观点和经验"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:20
msgid "Giving and gracefully accepting constructive feedback"
msgstr "给予并优雅地接受建设性的反馈"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:21
msgid ""
"Accepting responsibility and apologizing to those affected by our "
"mistakes, and learning from the experience"
msgstr "承担责任并向受我们错误影响的人道歉，并从中吸取教训"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:22
msgid ""
"Focusing on what is best not just for us as individuals, but for the "
"overall community"
msgstr "不仅关注我们个人，更关注对整个社区最有利的事情"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:24
msgid "Examples of unacceptable behavior include:"
msgstr "不可接受的行为示例包括："

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:27
msgid ""
"The use of sexualized language or imagery, and sexual attention or "
"advances of any kind"
msgstr "使用性化语言或图像，以及任何形式的性关注或性暗示"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:28
msgid ""
"Trolling, insulting or derogatory comments, and personal or political "
"attacks"
msgstr "挑衅、侮辱或贬损性评论，以及人身或政治攻击"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:29
msgid "Public or private harassment"
msgstr "公开或私下的骚扰"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:30
msgid ""
"Publishing others' private information, such as a physical or email "
"address, without their explicit permission"
msgstr "未经他人明确许可发布他人的私人信息，如物理地址或电子邮件地址"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:31
msgid ""
"Other conduct which could reasonably be considered inappropriate in a "
"professional setting"
msgstr "在专业环境中可能合理被视为不适当的其他行为"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:34
msgid "Enforcement Responsibilities"
msgstr "执行责任"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:36
msgid ""
"Community leaders are responsible for clarifying and enforcing our "
"standards of acceptable behavior and will take appropriate and fair "
"corrective action in response to any behavior that they deem "
"inappropriate, threatening, offensive, or harmful."
msgstr ""
"社区领导者负责澄清和执行我们的可接受行为标准，"
"并将对他们认为不适当、威胁性、冒犯性或有害的行为采取适当和公平的纠正措施。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:38
msgid ""
"Community leaders have the right and responsibility to remove, edit, or "
"reject comments, commits, code, wiki edits, issues, and other "
"contributions that are not aligned to this Code of Conduct, and will "
"communicate reasons for moderation decisions when appropriate."
msgstr ""
"社区领导者有权并有责任删除、编辑或拒绝不符合本行为准则的评论、"
"提交、代码、wiki 编辑、问题和其他贡献，并在适当的时候沟通审核决定的理由。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:41
msgid "Scope"
msgstr "范围"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:43
msgid ""
"This Code of Conduct applies within all community spaces, and also "
"applies when an individual is officially representing the community in "
"public spaces. Examples of representing our community include using an "
"official e-mail address, posting via an official social media account, or"
" acting as an appointed representative at an online or offline event."
msgstr ""
"本行为准则适用于所有社区空间，也适用于个人在公共场所正式代表社区时。"
"代表我们社区的示例包括使用官方电子邮件地址、通过官方社交媒体账户发帖，"
"或作为指定代表参加线上或线下活动。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:46
msgid "Enforcement"
msgstr "执行"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:48
msgid ""
"Instances of abusive, harassing, or otherwise unacceptable behavior may "
"be reported to the community leaders responsible for enforcement at "
"zhuchongjing_pypi@163.com. All complaints will be reviewed and "
"investigated promptly and fairly."
msgstr ""
"辱骂、骚扰或其他不可接受的行为实例可以报告给负责执行的社区领导者，"
"邮箱为 zhuchongjing_pypi@163.com。所有投诉都将得到及时和公正的审查和调查。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:50
msgid ""
"All community leaders are obligated to respect the privacy and security "
"of the reporter of any incident."
msgstr "所有社区领导者都有义务尊重任何事件报告者的隐私和安全。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:53
msgid "Enforcement Guidelines"
msgstr "执行指南"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:55
msgid ""
"Community leaders will follow these Community Impact Guidelines in "
"determining the consequences for any action they deem in violation of "
"this Code of Conduct:"
msgstr ""
"社区领导者将遵循这些社区影响指南，"
"来确定他们认为违反本行为准则的任何行为的后果："

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:58
msgid "1. Correction"
msgstr "1. 纠正"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:60
msgid ""
"**Community Impact**\\ : Use of inappropriate language or other behavior "
"deemed unprofessional or unwelcome in the community."
msgstr ""
"**社区影响**\\ ：使用不恰当的语言或其他被认为不专业或不受欢迎的行为。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:62
msgid ""
"**Consequence**\\ : A private, written warning from community leaders, "
"providing clarity around the nature of the violation and an explanation "
"of why the behavior was inappropriate. A public apology may be requested."
msgstr ""
"**后果**\\ ：来自社区领导者的私人书面警告，明确违规性质并解释该行为为何不恰当。"
"可能会要求公开道歉。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:65
msgid "2. Warning"
msgstr "2. 警告"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:67
msgid ""
"**Community Impact**\\ : A violation through a single incident or series "
"of actions."
msgstr "**社区影响**\\ ：通过单一事件或一系列行为造成的违规。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:69
msgid ""
"**Consequence**\\ : A warning with consequences for continued behavior. "
"No interaction with the people involved, including unsolicited "
"interaction with those enforcing the Code of Conduct, for a specified "
"period of time. This includes avoiding interactions in community spaces "
"as well as external channels like social media. Violating these terms may"
" lead to a temporary or permanent ban."
msgstr ""
"**后果**\\ ：对持续行为的后果发出警告。在指定时间内不得与相关人员互动，"
"包括未经请求与执行行为准则的人员互动。这包括避免在社区空间以及社交媒体等外部渠道中互动。"
"违反这些条款可能导致临时或永久封禁。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:72
msgid "3. Temporary Ban"
msgstr "3. 临时封禁"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:74
msgid ""
"**Community Impact**\\ : A serious violation of community standards, "
"including sustained inappropriate behavior."
msgstr "**社区影响**\\ ：严重违反社区标准，包括持续的不当行为。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:76
msgid ""
"**Consequence**\\ : A temporary ban from any sort of interaction or "
"public communication with the community for a specified period of time. "
"No public or private interaction with the people involved, including "
"unsolicited interaction with those enforcing the Code of Conduct, is "
"allowed during this period. Violating these terms may lead to a permanent"
" ban."
msgstr ""
"**后果**\\ ：在指定时间内禁止与社区进行任何形式的互动或公开交流。"
"在此期间，不允许与相关人员进行公开或私下互动，包括未经请求与执行行为准则的人员互动。"
"违反这些条款可能导致永久封禁。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:79
msgid "4. Permanent Ban"
msgstr "4. 永久封禁"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:81
msgid ""
"**Community Impact**\\ : Demonstrating a pattern of violation of "
"community standards, including sustained inappropriate behavior, "
"harassment of an individual, or aggression toward or disparagement of "
"classes of individuals."
msgstr ""
"**社区影响**\\ ：表现出违反社区标准的行为模式，包括持续的不当行为、"
"骚扰个人，或对某类人群进行攻击或贬低。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:83
msgid ""
"**Consequence**\\ : A permanent ban from any sort of public interaction "
"within the community."
msgstr "**后果**\\ ：永久禁止在社区内进行任何形式的公开互动。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:86
msgid "Attribution"
msgstr "归属"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:88
msgid ""
"This Code of Conduct is adapted from the Contributor Covenant, version "
"2.1, available at `Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct <https://www"
".contributor-covenant.org/version/2/1/code_of_conduct.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"本行为准则改编自贡献者公约 2.1 版，"
"可在 `贡献者公约行为准则 <https://www.contributor-covenant.org/version/2/1/code_of_conduct.html>`_ 获取。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:90
msgid ""
"Community Impact Guidelines were inspired by Mozilla's code of conduct "
"enforcement ladder."
msgstr "社区影响指南的灵感来源于 Mozilla 的行为准则执行阶梯。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:92
msgid ""
"For answers to common questions about this code of conduct, see "
"`Frequently Asked Questions <https://www.contributor-covenant.org/faq>`_."
msgstr ""
"关于本行为准则的常见问题的解答，"
"请参阅 `常见问题 <https://www.contributor-covenant.org/faq>`_。"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:95
msgid "Contact Information"
msgstr "联系信息"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:97
msgid "For reporting issues or seeking clarification:"
msgstr "如需报告问题或寻求澄清："

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:100
msgid "**Email**\\ : zhuchongjing_pypi@163.com"
msgstr "**电子邮件**\\ ：zhuchongjing_pypi@163.com"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:101
msgid "**GitHub Issues**\\ : Use the appropriate issue template"
msgstr "**GitHub Issues**\\ ：使用适当的问题模板"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:102
msgid "**Community Discussions**\\ : GitHub Discussions forum"
msgstr "**社区讨论**\\ ：GitHub Discussions 论坛"

#: ../../../CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md:104
msgid ""
"We are committed to maintaining a respectful and inclusive community "
"where everyone can contribute and learn."
msgstr ""
"我们致力于维护一个相互尊重、包容的社区，让每个人都能贡献和学习。"
